<br>
As far as the whiners who gripe about posts being hijacked, get over it. It takes far less effort to post something to get it back on track than to bitch about starting a new thread. We have all done it to some extent, but the imprtant threads, unlike those that are just nonsensical flaming, usually make it back on track if anyone really cares enough to bother.<br>
<br>
I too am a conservative, and could give a @#%$ if anyone cares or not. I will continue to speak out when things are unfair, or if I have a really strong opinion. I find it a shame that a nice person such as Jynn felt the need to leave, but we all have to decide if we can be a part of this particular board community or not. I choose to stay as I enjoy the people here. Some impress me one day, and make me want to rip the power cord from my monitor the next.<br>
<br>
We will not all agree all the time on all things, and I hope that you may come back someday to visit us again Jynn.<br>
<br>
