Nope, not at all.  Actually, I think this is the proper place because it will turn into a flame session and that saves someone else from having to move it later.  FWIW  I may not always agree with your point of view, but you at least set forth an intelligent and articulate one as opposed to a string of personal x-rated attacks.<br>
