Thank you.  I count you as one of my new friends.  You remind me much of Snowbyrd.  Your personality suits your character well.<br>
<br>
I'll probably be posting some short stories on the Vinceremo board later.  I will take this opportunity to thank you for your interest in The Bard.  It started out as an introduction of Mynxx to Vinceremo and turned into a story.  Several people have encouraged me with the story so it is now being rewritten into a real novel sans the EQ aspects.  I can't finish the murder mystery until I go to Louisiana for some research, so this will be a pleasant diversion.  My sincere gratitude to you and the others for making me want to delve a little deeper into the fantasy.<br>
<br>
<br>
&quot;Some impress me one day, and make me want to rip the power cord from my monitor the next.&quot;<br>
