Hmmm.  I know the feeling.  In reality, I find quite a few of the people here quite interesting.  There are some very witty people here.  I enjoy most of the things Sem passes along.  There are some intriguing personalities here.  <br>
<br>
&quot;They didnt slam her for having an opinion, they slamed her opinion.&quot;<br>
